		<title>10 Key Trends &#038; Insights to Inform Your 2026 Marketing Planning</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/2026-marketing-planning</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Stephanie Heitman]]></dc:creator>
