										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>January. For some, it&#8217;s the holiday let-down season. For others, it&#8217;s the Monday of months. For us (and soon to be you), it&#8217;s the month of marketing opportunities! There&#8217;s Vision Board Day, National Mentoring Month, Squirrel Appreciation Day, and so much more!</p>
<p>In this article, we&#8217;re sharing a full list of January awareness themes, holidays, and national days, tons of creative ways to use them for unique and meaningful marketing, and marketing planning tips and ideas to stay successful all year.</p>
