<div id="january"></div>
<h2>January 2025</h2>
<p>In the first month of the year, make a splash with these ideas by adding them to your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/marketing-calendar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2025 marketing calendar</a>.</p>
<h3>January marketing and promotion ideas</h3>
<ul>
<li>Run a 25% off sale to celebrate the year 2025.</li>
<li>Make <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/small-business-marketing-resolutions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">New Year‚Äôs resolutions for your business</a>, and if applicable, share them with your customers on social media or through email marketing. (Get more <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/new-years-social-media-posts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">New Year&#8217;s social media post ideas</a> here!)</li>
<li>Host or attend a blood drive as a company‚ÄìJanuary is National Blood Drive Month.</li>
<li>Write a holiday or <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/12/08/year-in-review-email-examples" rel="noopener">year-end round-up post</a> for your company blog or social sites‚Äìinclude pictures of how you and your team celebrated.</li>
<li>Check on your <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/geo-targeting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">local PPC ads</a> to make sure you&#8217;re bidding for the right keywords to start off 2025 strong. (Or get started running local PPC if you&#8217;re not already!)</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-153265" src="https://localiq.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/january-social-media-holidays-blood-donor-month.jpg" alt="january social media holidays - instagram post about why donate blood from hospital" width="936" height="554" /></p>
<h3>January social media calendar ideas</h3>
<p>Here are some key <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/january-social-media-holidays-and-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">January social media holidays</a> and observances,¬† plus <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/12/07/january-marketing-ideas">January</a> hashtags to incorporate into your 2025 <a href="https://localiq.com/products/social-media-marketing/?&amp;itm_source=localiq&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links">social media marketing</a> calendar.</p>
<p><strong>Jan 8: Bubble Bath Day</strong></p>
<p>Post a quote about self-care and encourage your audience to take some time for themselves. #BubbleBathDay</p>
<p><strong>Jan 13: Make Your Dream Come True Day</strong></p>
<p>Share how you or one of your team members has had a dream come true‚Äìwhether it‚Äôs a goal you reached, a milestone you celebrated, or a trip to Disneyland! Ask your audience what dream they want to come true this year. #DreamComeTrue</p>
<p><strong>Jan 20: Martin Luther King Jr. Day</strong></p>
<p>Celebrate this day by sharing your favorite Martin Luther King Jr. quote and asking your audience to share theirs. #MLKDay</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2025-marketing-calendar-january-scaled-1.webp" alt="january 2025 marketing calendar" width="2560" height="1595" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-87760" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2025-marketing-calendar-january-scaled-1.webp 2560w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2025-marketing-calendar-january-scaled-1-1280x798.webp 1280w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2025-marketing-calendar-january-scaled-1-980x611.webp 980w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2025-marketing-calendar-january-scaled-1-480x299.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) and (max-width: 1280px) 1280px, (min-width: 1281px) 2560px, 100vw" /></p>
