<h3>June marketing calendar ideas</h3>
<ul>
<li>We‚Äôre halfway through the year‚Äìare you on track to hit your business and <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/marketing-plan-goals-objectives-for-small-businesses/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">marketing goals</a>? Review the goals you set and adjust as needed.</li>
<li>Run a summer sale or promotion to get more people to try out your business. Make sure to promote it with email marketing. (Try out one of these <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/june-email-subject-lines/">June email subject lines</a> to increase opens!)</li>
<li>Consider testing out a new <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/06/12/marketing-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">marketing strategy</a> in the last half of the year‚Äìresearch some options or talk to your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/marketing/5-questions-to-ask-your-marketing-partner/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">marketing partner</a> for ideas.</li>
