<h2>July 2025</h2>
<p>Heat up your marketing calendar planning with these hot tips and creative marketing ideas for July.</p>
<h3>July marketing and promotion ideas</h3>
<ul>
<li>Run a special Fourth of July sale or promotion to get more people to visit your business this month. (Use these <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/july-email-subject-lines/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">July email subject lines</a> to help boost your promotions!)</li>
