<h2>August 2025</h2>
<p>As we get into the back half of the year, don‚Äôt let your marketing and promotions slip away. Use these <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/07/08/august-marketing-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noopener">August marketing ideas</a> to capture those back-to-school searchers and end-of-summer customers.</p>
<h3>August marketing ideas</h3>
<ul>
<li>It‚Äôs the back-to-school season! Run a <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/back-to-school-marketing-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">back-to-school promotion</a> or contest to reach students and their parents.</li>
<li>Don&#8217;t forget about social media&#8211;Any business can get in the back-to-school spirit on social media with the right <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/back-to-school-instagram-captions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">back-to-school Instagram captions</a>.</li>
<li>It‚Äôs not too early to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/when-should-you-start-holiday-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">start thinking about your holiday marketing plan</a>‚Äìoutline your specials and promotions now and let your marketing partner know what you‚Äôre planning.</li>
<li>Everyone likes a good pen or tote bag‚Äìconsider giving out promotional materials to your customers to stay top-of-mind.</li>
<li>To help meet your year-end goals, check in on your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/what-is-lead-management/">lead management</a> system. Is it working for you? Or do you need to revisit some other options?</li>
