<li>Check in with your employees to confirm when or if anyone is planning to take off for the upcoming holidays so your scheduling is streamlined.</li>
<li>Make sure to send holiday emails with your promotions, sales, and events. (Use these <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/holiday-email-templates/">holiday email templates</a> and <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/holiday-email-subject-lines/">subject lines</a>.)</li>
<li>Send appreciation messages to thank your customers for their business over the last year. (Use these <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/customer-appreciation-ideas/">customer appreciation ideas</a> for inspiration!)</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-147688" src="https://localiq.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/small-business-saturday-ideas-partner-with-local-businesses.jpg" alt="partner with other small businesses for your small business saturday marketing" width="747" height="668" /></p>
