		<title>NEW Advertising Benchmarks for Real Estate in 2021</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/08/31/real-estate-advertising-benchmarks</link>
					<comments>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/08/31/real-estate-advertising-benchmarks#respond</comments>
		
