<h3><strong>Data sources</strong></h3>
<p>This data was pulled from a sample of 2,690 North American-based LOCALiQ client accounts in the real estate vertical who were running search advertising, display advertising, and/or social media advertising between March 1, 2020, and April 25, 2021. Each subcategory includes at minimum 10 unique active clients. ‚ÄúAverages‚Äù are technically median figures to account for outliers. All currency values are posted in USD.</p>
